    AgeOff

    An AgeOffFromDays is a BiPredicate that ages off old data based on a provided age off time in days.

    An CollectionContains is a Predicate that checks if a Collection contains a provided value.
    Exists
    An Exists is a Predicate that simply checks the input object is not null.

    IsA
    An IsA Predicate tests whether an input Object is an instance of a given control Class.
    IsEqual
    An IsEqual is a Predicate that checks that the input is equal to a control value.
    IsFalse
    An IsFalse is a Predicate that checks that the input boolean is false.
    IsIn
    An IsIn is a Predicate that checks that the input is in a set of allowed values.
    IsLessThan
    An IsLessThan is a Predicate that checks that the input Comparable is less than a control value.
    IsLongerThan
    An IsLongerThan is a Predicate that checks that the input object has a length more than a minimum length.
    IsMoreThan
    An IsMoreThan is a Predicate that checks that the input Comparable is more than a control value.
    IsShorterThan
    An IsShorterThan is a Predicate that checks that the input object has a length less than a maximum length.
    IsTrue
    An IsTrue is a Predicate that checks that the input boolean is true.
    IsXLessThanY
    An IsXLessThanY is a BiPredicate that checks that the first input Comparable is less than the second input Comparable.
    IsXMoreThanY
    An IsXMoreThanY is a BiPredicate that checks that the first input Comparable is more than the second input Comparable.
    MapContains
    An MapContains is a Predicate that checks whether a Map contains a provided key.
    MapContainsPredicate
    An MapContainsPredicate is a Predicate that checks whether a Map contains a key that matches a given predicate.
    MultiRegex

    Not<I>
